videos.description: Justice Hansen completes a pass to Justin McInnis who adds a long run for a 71-yard gain. The Red Wolves would later score on the drive.
videos.headline: McInnis rips off long catch and run for Arkansas St.

videos.description: Warren Wand runs past multiple defenders in this long touchdown run to tie the game in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Arkansas State's Wand breaks for 82-yard TD run

videos.description: Quarterback Justin Hansen keeps the ball and runs up the middle for a 38-yard score to extend the Red Wolves' lead.
videos.headline: Arkansas State extends lead with Hansen TD

videos.description: Marcus Green returns the kickoff 95-yards for a touchdown to cut Arkansas State's lead.
videos.headline: UL Monroe answers with kickoff return TD

videos.description: Caleb Evans finds an open RJ Turner in the end zone for a 27-yard touchdown pass in the 3rd quarter.
